  "2201910": {
    "name": "亡魂战纪",
    "steam_appid": 2201910,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/4b94d7f325e33c8a92328e9c8b2a1f00.avif?t=1765186536\" width=616 height=106 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌控元素奥义，挥舞利刃重器，魔法与兵器的自由组合将衍生无限连招可能！自定义专属战斗风格，迎战机制各异、压迫感拉满的强敌与首领。每一场对决都是操作与策略的双重考验，胜负只在电光石火之间。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/c197c52ddec8ae514ad0a21a7bbc514f.poster.avif?t=1765186536\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/c197c52ddec8ae514ad0a21a7bbc514f.webm?t=1765186536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/c197c52ddec8ae514ad0a21a7bbc514f.mp4?t=1765186536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/99ad0ee0d8652f279a9f04da3d4dcb34.avif?t=1765186536\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从静谧苍林到元素狂乱的焦土，每个区域都暗藏独特危机与叙事伏笔。解锁攀岩、滑翔等专属能力，即可开拓新路径，在错落景观中寻觅隐藏通道、捷径与远古馈赠。探索的每一步都藏着惊喜，每一处废墟都在诉说过往。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/1842db7e7a8ec9aff54242134e25820e.poster.avif?t=1765186536\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/1842db7e7a8ec9aff54242134e25820e.webm?t=1765186536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/1842db7e7a8ec9aff54242134e25820e.mp4?t=1765186536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/bbff3e78fd841e6e5348a47130831a36.avif?t=1765186536\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数种神兵散落世间，每柄武器都自带不可复制的专属特性。通过击败敌人积累素材，升级解锁专属属性，自由混搭武器与魔法，打造贴合自身风格的战斗构建，让每一次挥击都尽显专属锋芒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/906aa584e41661eb04dd56625fe76c55.poster.avif?t=1765186536\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/906aa584e41661eb04dd56625fe76c55.webm?t=1765186536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/906aa584e41661eb04dd56625fe76c55.mp4?t=1765186536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/8d17cda6cfb95e27c226940492e42fde.avif?t=1765186536\" width=616 height=106 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这趟冒险不止于战斗，更是对世界破碎根源的深度追问。深入被遗忘的文明遗址，与性格鲜明的角色互动，解读环境中暗藏的叙事线索，逐步拼凑出远古力量的起源、同伴遇险的真相，以及你与这个世界的宿命联结。剧情跌宕起伏、情感层层递进，你的选择将牵动角色命运，最终揭开一段充满遗憾与救赎的奇幻史诗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/7d5a7aca8592fefe401cf972e6e6c9d8.poster.avif?t=1765186536\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/7d5a7aca8592fefe401cf972e6e6c9d8.webm?t=1765186536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201910/extras/7d5a7aca8592fefe401cf972e6e6c9d8.mp4?t=1765186536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>其乐id：1706296</p>",
